# 4. Normalization Layer

Semua output engine dikonversi ke skala 0â€“100.

Rumus umum:

```
NormalizedValue = 
((RawValue - MinReference) / (MaxReference - MinReference)) Ã— 100
```

Tujuan:

* Standarisasi lintas sistem
* Memudahkan agregasi
* Memungkinkan simulasi

---

# 5. Game Core Engine

Semua stat karakter berasal dari 5 indeks inti:

| Core Metric | Sumber        |
| ----------- | ------------- |
| Vitality    | Bazi + ZWDS   |
| Momentum    | Qi Men        |
| Stability   | Feng Shui     |
| Fortune     | ZWDS + Qi Men |
| Volatility  | I Ching + Sha |

