# 9. Enemy Generator System

Enemy muncul jika:

```
Volatility + ElementClashScore + ShaImpact 
> Threshold
```

Jenis Enemy:

| Tipe           | Sumber                      |
| -------------- | --------------------------- |
| Element Foe    | Elemen lawan DM             |
| Direction Boss | Wu Huang / San Sha          |
| Time Wraith    | Jam buruk                   |
| Palace Crisis  | Rumah terkena bintang buruk |

